This business trust company said its board elected Kieran E. Burke, a consultant to Drexel Burnham Lambert Group Inc., as chief executive officer, a new post, and as president.
Mr. Burke succeeds Richard D. Manley, who will remain as a consultant to the company.
Both men were unavailable to comment.
The company also named Michael E. Gellert, a director and a major shareholder, to fill the vacant seat of chairman. 

